          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Government Refusal of Abortion in Contracting and Enterprise or the GRACE Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits a federal entity from entering into a contract with a person or entity that donates or matches employee donations to Planned Parenthood Federation of America, Inc.,&nbsp;or any of its affiliates or clinics. This prohibition applies to contracts entered into after the enactment of this Act and to subcontracts (at any tier) awarded under such contracts. </p>]]></text>
